Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:16.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,颯太
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.60,0:00:21.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:24.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,難得來度假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.59,0:00:26.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,試試去約個女孩怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:29.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,誰都不會理像我這樣的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.91,0:00:31.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,還是睡午覺讓我感覺更安逸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:36.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,帽子？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:44.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:48.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:50.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.14,0:00:53.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.56,0:00:54.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:59.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,吶  和我一起玩遊戲嗎
